{
  "id": "com.applemusic.source",
  "name": "Apple Music",
  "versionCode": 2,
  "versionName": "0.1.1",
  "author": "Replica0110",
  "description": "Apple Music 搜索源插件",
  "apiVersion": 1,
  "includeDirs": ["lib"],
  "icon": "icon.png",
  "entry": "source.js",
  "capabilities": ["searchSongs", "getLyrics", "searchCovers"],
  "requiredHostApis": [
    "app.userAgent",
    "runtime.info",
    "http.getText",
    "http.postText",
    "http.get",
    "http.post"
  ],
  "configFields": [
    {
      "key": "lyrics_provider_notice",
      "title": "歌词源说明",
      "group": "歌词",
      "type": "markdown",
      "defaultValue": "### 歌词源说明\n\n- **第三方**：通过 [PaxSenix Apple Music Lyrics](https://lyrics.paxsenix.org/apple-music/lyrics) 获取歌词，不需要 Apple Music 登录态。\n- **官方**：通过 Apple Music 官方接口获取歌词，需要填写网页登录态 Cookie 中的 `media-user-token`。\n\n官方源限制：\n\n- `media-user-token` 所属地区需要与下方选择的地区一致。\n- `media-user-token` 会过期，失效后需要重新获取。\n- 高频请求或批量匹配可能触发 Apple 风控、限流或临时封禁。\n- 只有账号和地区有权限访问的歌曲才可能返回官方歌词。"
    },
    {
      "key": "lyrics_provider",
      "title": "歌词源",
      "group": "歌词",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "third_party",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "third_party",
          "label": "第三方"
        },
        {
          "value": "official",
          "label": "官方"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "media_user_token",
      "title": "Media User Token",
      "group": "歌词",
      "type": "password",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "",
      "dependency": {
        "match": { "key": "lyrics_provider", "value": "official" }
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "region",
      "title": "地区",
      "summary": "用于 Apple Music 请求的语言/地区参数",
      "group": "请求",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "zh-CN",
      "options": [
        { "value": "zh-CN", "label": "中国大陆", "summary": "zh-CN" },
        { "value": "en-US", "label": "美国", "summary": "en-US" },
        { "value": "ja-JP", "label": "日本", "summary": "ja-JP" },
        { "value": "ko-KR", "label": "韩国", "summary": "ko-KR" },
        { "value": "tr-TR", "label": "土耳其", "summary": "tr-TR" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "cover_size",
      "title": "封面大小",
      "summary": "Apple Music 封面图片尺寸",
      "group": "封面",
      "type": "dropdown",
      "required": true,
      "defaultValue": "3000",
      "options": [
        { "value": "500", "label": "500 × 500" },
        { "value": "1000", "label": "1000 × 1000" },
        { "value": "3000", "label": "3000 × 3000" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "metadataFields": [
    {
      "key": "title",
      "title": "歌曲标题",
      "group": "基本信息",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "TITLE",
      "defaultMode": "OVERWRITE"
    },
    {
      "key": "artist",
      "title": "艺术家",
      "group": "基本信息",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "ARTIST",
      "defaultMode": "OVERWRITE"
    },
    {
      "key": "album",
      "title": "专辑名",
      "group": "基本信息",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "ALBUM",
      "defaultMode": "OVERWRITE"
    },
    {
      "key": "date",
      "title": "发行日期",
      "group": "基本信息",
      "type": "date",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "DATE",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "track_number",
      "title": "音轨号",
      "group": "基本信息",
      "type": "number",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "TRACK_NUMBER",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "disc_number",
      "title": "碟片号",
      "group": "基本信息",
      "type": "number",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "DISC_NUMBER",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "cover_url",
      "title": "封面图片",
      "group": "媒体",
      "type": "url",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "COVER",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "composer",
      "title": "作曲",
      "group": "制作信息",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "COMPOSER",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "lyricist",
      "title": "作词",
      "group": "制作信息",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "LYRICIST",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "genre",
      "title": "流派",
      "group": "扩展",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": true,
      "defaultTarget": "GENRE",
      "defaultMode": "SUPPLEMENT"
    },
    {
      "key": "apple_id",
      "title": "Apple ID",
      "group": "内部",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": false,
      "internal": true,
      "defaultTarget": "CUSTOM",
      "defaultMode": "DISABLED"
    },
    {
      "key": "album_id",
      "title": "Apple 专辑ID",
      "group": "内部",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": false,
      "internal": true,
      "defaultTarget": "CUSTOM",
      "defaultMode": "DISABLED"
    },
    {
      "key": "play_params_id",
      "title": "Apple 播放参数ID",
      "group": "内部",
      "type": "text",
      "writeable": false,
      "internal": true,
      "defaultTarget": "CUSTOM",
      "defaultMode": "DISABLED"
    }
  ]
}
